OL,3,CStarmer insists digital ID will never
OL,4,Cbe used to put Brits under surveillance
OL,6,FWatch: Keir Starmer takes questions on
OL,7,Fdigital ID in bid to dispel
OL,8,F'misinformation'
OL,10,FKeir Starmer has insisted digital ID
OL,11,Fwill not be used to track every aspect
OL,12,Fof a person's life, and the scheme
OL,13,Fwon't expand to a social scoring
OL,14,Fsystem like the one used in China.
OL,16,FThe prime minister has been taking
OL,17,Fquestions on digital ID in a bid to
OL,18,Fdispel what Number 10 says is
OL,19,Fmisinformation and conspiracy theories
OL,20,Fabout the policy, which is opposed by
OL,21,Fmillions of people in the UK.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/7
