OL,3,CStarmer insists digital ID will never
OL,4,Cbe used to put Brits under surveillance
OL,6,FThe policy was originally announced as
OL,7,Fpart of plans to cut the number of
OL,8,Fasylum seekers arriving in the UK by
OL,9,Fmaking it harder for them to work here
OL,10,Fillegally.
OL,12,FStarmer said there will be many other
OL,13,Fbenefits to digital ID cards, such as
OL,14,Fmaking it easier for people to access
OL,15,Fpublic services like the NHS or prove
OL,16,Fwho they are when doing things like
OL,17,Ftaking out a mortgage.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/7
