OL,3,CStarmer insists digital ID will never
OL,4,Cbe used to put Brits under surveillance
OL,6,FBut talking about those other
OL,7,Ffunctions has led people to question
OL,8,Fwhether digital ID uses would be
OL,9,Fexpanded in future, for example, to
OL,10,Ftrack how often people fly or eat meat.
OL,12,F"This is just a false rumour," he
OL,13,Fsaid. "There's absolutely nothing in
OL,14,Fit. No plans to do it, nor should
OL,15,Fthere be. This is basic information.
OL,16,FWho you are, what your age is. That
OL,17,Fsort of information, the stuff that we
OL,18,Fneed every day, to prove who we are."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/7
