OL,3,CStarmer insists digital ID will never
OL,4,Cbe used to put Brits under surveillance
OL,6,FAsked how he could be sure future
OL,7,Fgovernments wouldn't expand the scheme
OL,8,Fto surveil their citizens, he said:
OL,9,F"This law will have to be set out in
OL,10,Fprimary legislation and therefore,
OL,11,Fit'll all be set out in law, what the
OL,12,Flimits are, how it's controlled, and
OL,13,Fthat'll be voted for in Parliament.
