OL,3,CStarmer insists digital ID will never
OL,4,Cbe used to put Brits under surveillance
OL,6,F"So it will be in stone that this is
OL,7,Fthe system and you can't simply change
OL,8,Fit, because it's in law."
OL,10,FA previous Labour prime minister, Tony
OL,11,FBlair, tried to introduce a similar
OL,12,Fnational ID card for everyone living
OL,13,Fin the UK but was forced to back down
OL,14,Famid intense opposition.
OL,16,FBut Starmer insists he's committed to
OL,17,Fpressing ahead, despite the huge
OL,18,Fnumbers against digital ID cards, and
OL,19,Fhas promised to introduce them by the
OL,20,Fnext election.
